5. Program to show static variable shared across objects but instance variable not.
-->class Demo {
        static int shared = 0;
        int individual = 0;
    
        void increment() {
            shared++;
            individual++;
        }
    
        void display() {
            System.out.println("Shared: " + shared + ", Individual: " + individual);
        }
    
        public static void main(String[] args) {
            Demo obj1 = new Demo();
            Demo obj2 = new Demo();
    
            obj1.increment();
            obj2.increment();
    
            obj1.display();
            obj2.display();
        }
    }
    ✔ Output
    Shared: 2, Individual: 1
    Shared: 2, Individual: 1
    👉 Static is shared, instance is separate


